  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play games of Russian roulette with a major strategic component; you can load your own bullets. Choose bullets that can damage, protect, heal, and more. Between rounds, plan and prepare your approach by buying bullets or items that could help you later. Use your progress to unlock buffs for your subsequent runs and try your best to make it as far as you can.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fire Bullets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fire bullets at yourself and take a risk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/f11c834f01e3bedd42c7ee6080be237c.poster.avif?t=1741051987\" width=800 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/f11c834f01e3bedd42c7ee6080be237c.webm?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/f11c834f01e3bedd42c7ee6080be237c.mp4?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pass Bullets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pass to skip the bullet entirely.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/685e38f2ac52bd5db8796026444161c2.poster.avif?t=1741051987\" width=800 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/685e38f2ac52bd5db8796026444161c2.webm?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/685e38f2ac52bd5db8796026444161c2.mp4?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Hand Over Bullets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand over to make your opponent take the bullet; but beware it may backfire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/76f9abafd0e29bfdefbb0398178e4cf1.poster.avif?t=1741051987\" width=800 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/76f9abafd0e29bfdefbb0398178e4cf1.webm?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/76f9abafd0e29bfdefbb0398178e4cf1.mp4?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play games of Russian roulette with a major strategic component; you can load your own bullets. Choose bullets that can damage, protect, heal, and more. Between rounds, plan and prepare your approach by buying bullets or items that could help you later. Use your progress to unlock buffs for your subsequent runs and try your best to make it as far as you can.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fire Bullets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fire bullets at yourself and take a risk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/f11c834f01e3bedd42c7ee6080be237c.poster.avif?t=1741051987\" width=800 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/f11c834f01e3bedd42c7ee6080be237c.webm?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/f11c834f01e3bedd42c7ee6080be237c.mp4?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pass Bullets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pass to skip the bullet entirely.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/685e38f2ac52bd5db8796026444161c2.poster.avif?t=1741051987\" width=800 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/685e38f2ac52bd5db8796026444161c2.webm?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/685e38f2ac52bd5db8796026444161c2.mp4?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Hand Over Bullets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand over to make your opponent take the bullet; but beware it may backfire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/76f9abafd0e29bfdefbb0398178e4cf1.poster.avif?t=1741051987\" width=800 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/76f9abafd0e29bfdefbb0398178e4cf1.webm?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500250/extras/76f9abafd0e29bfdefbb0398178e4cf1.mp4?t=1741051987\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
